Ectstasis 
*Note: it would make more sense to change the suffix of poiesis to something else*
Migration of a CVector to a CNode or Body outside of an established body. 
	Autopoiesis
	Poiesis that takes place within an existing body
	Allopoiesis 
	Creation of a new separate body
	Practopoiesis
	Creation of a sub-body
	Sympoiesis 
	Multi-body origin, collective on of systems without obviously defined boundaries
