# Concepts
**Praxis:**

- Always use all [your] skills to benefit them individually and as a group.  
    _(Makeup â†’ Sales â†’ Networking? Photography â†’ Dating profile/CV/social media?)_

All foes have natures that, once ascertained, may be undermined and exploited. The more the germ incorporates the DNA of thought (theoria) the more effective it is at the dissolution of related poiesis. How is a man's nature found out? How is a will tasted? Go into their midst, find the inferior and the uniformed. Watch the process of mentoring, 3:1 study of good to evil. Learn their ways and thoughts from their internal dialogue. Test the pH of an idea by pouring it upon group conversations or upoon the relationships. Extreme pH disolves bonds, but may not spread. Better to think of germs than chemisty? 

Dilemma: A blatant lesson is often ignored, nowadays resented. The truth is worth anything, everything. Be fearless in the pursuit of truth, but wise when plotting your course. The parable, the conundrum, the question whose answer is many truths, value that saying. Break the realest taboos, not he fictive ones. A dilemma must always be one. A conundrum is always explored when more voices engage in the conversation. Unforeseen consequences always follow. Foreseen consequences are at times a mirage. High stakes, high interest, but do not disappoint it, nor spoil it. Let the accuser break their own taboo. Break your audience when you have them in your grasp. Anyone may speak, but everyone listens to a powerful voice. How does one destroy the notion of acceptable discourse? what drives such a thing? Who must go? How do you light the fire beneath them? How does one turn the whale? What are the vunrabilities in AD structure? What are the charges, where do they go, and when do they go off? Let us dig a grave. Choose a powerson to save based on generalized information: learn the bias of the player, the character override teaches the audience about the character and their development, the others are graphically murdered. Do not worry, this is a completely routine and morally acceptable procedure in your time zone, abortion I mean. Of a man, of a thought. 

Nodal Recursion
Nodal recursion is a common trap of culture of philosophy. A theoric focus precipitates many theoria.
EX: Doctrinal Recursion: literalism, scientism, fundamentalism, Catholicism; in each instance doctrinal recursion generates an abundance of major and minor doctrine.
EX: Praxic Recursion: skepticism, Hinduism, pantheism
The cause of culture and worldview formation.
 
Symposium 

Art 
Shit is art and vice versa, but how do you justify high art? Poiesis. 

Parentage
Parentage matters for consideration and display. For example, a generative process may involve answering multiple concurrent questions whilst following multiple doctrines, informed by one or more theoria, but that does not mean each of the contributing doctrine/praxic/theoria are conjoined or even concurrent! When a set of ideas overlap that overlap they may be the result of one similar node or many. It may be similarly rather than actual parentage. It really is similar to DNA in informational complexity, only it is like the RNA in a virus, with all sorts of intermixture and no clear parentage since there is no limitations on information exchange. 

Storytelling
Explaining a series of relationships is not defining relationships. It is a necessary component for communicating an idea and its confluences, but it is not the idea itself. Enter storytelling. the relationship between ideas is not, and is not described by storytelling, but storytelling is a useful tool for truncating the distance and keeping a listener engaged in the relational description. Storytelling is valuable as a communication tool but worthless on its own. It can also be a useful generative tool (praxic method), perhaps that is what it is? *does this represent a flaw in the model?*
Praxic discourse and poiestic outcomes are not mutually exclusive, but they have no relation in doctrine, not one that I see. Explaining rules or narrative is poieistic and praxic method, not a form of doctrine. 

Atomic Cnode
A singular origin Cnode which is necessary for the initiation of bodies.
